summary: Hey guys, you’re allowed to feel the way that you do about Dan and Phil but it’s completely unacceptable to fear monger and...
body:
Hey guys, you’re allowed to feel the way that you do about Dan and Phil but it’s completely unacceptable to fear monger and spread lies about things Dan and Phil have said or done. 

You have a right to be upset but when you fear monger and begin spreading lies to prove why you’re upset, you’re not helping the situation. You’re creating a toxic environment for everyone who follows you and believes what you’re saying. 

Please, think before you say something or post something. Think about what your followers might view your post as and think about how it might come across to everyone else. I know I’ve had this wake up call the last month but other people should as well. 

Creating a toxic environment for the sake of proving your point on why you’re upset with them is not okay. Please realize this.
